http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/kerala/MLAs-walk-out-of-function/article13983789.ece

: Three UDF MLAs walked out of the inaugural function of the Thrissur Revenue District Youth Festival in protest against the delay in starting the programme.C.N. Jayadeven, MP, who was to inaugurated the function, and Mayor Ajitha Jayarajan, who was to preside over the function, reached the venue an hour late. In protest against the delay, MLAs Therambil Ramakrishnan, P.A. Madhavan and T.N. Prathapan walked out of the function. They expressed their protest against lapse in proper organisation of the function. Mohiniyattam competition, which was to be conducted at the inaugural stage, also late.